6- I can add weight to the global font definition to win over the classes added by point 3 using !important

html {
    font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 100 !important;
}

7- I can change the background to green without changing the inline style using !important as in the previus exercise

.oh-no-inline-styles{
    background: green !important;
}